author: Ildefonso Ortiz
title: Coronavirus Fatalities in Mexico Rise to 273
description: Mexican health officials confirmed the continuing rise in the number of fatalities resulting from the spread of the novel coronavirus (COVID-19). In a single day, officials documented 40 fatalities bringing the new total to 273 since the start of the pandemic…
